Singer Timi Dakolo, paid a Surprise visit to Kolawola Ajeyemi, the husband of Actress Toyin Abraham on his 40th birthday. The Actress got Timi Dakolo, one of her husband’s favourite artistes to surprise him in the early hours of Monday, As he marks his 40th birthday. BBNaija Star Tuoyo Survives Car Accident in Lagos My Godfather Is the Richest Black Man, DJ Cuppy tells Kanye West She took to her Instagram page this morning, to share the video of Dakolo singing for her husband with the caption. “I got him@timidakolo is one of his favourites so I brought him home to wish Oko mi @kolawoleajeyemi happy birthday.”(sic) In the video, Timi Dakolo sang a birthday song for him and also sang a song from his Album “Everything”(AMEN), praying for Ajeyemi. The Actress just returned from the UK after the screening of her film,  “The Ghost and the Tour Too.”